#include<iostream>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
	int t, i, j, ar[6][6], found = false;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--){
        int row[6] = {0},col[6] = {0};
        
		found = 0;
		for(i=0;i<6;i++){
			for(j=0;j<6;j++){
				cin>>ar[i][j];
				if(ar[i][j]){
                    row[i] ++;
				    col[j] ++;
                }
			}
		}
		
		for(i=0;i<6;i++){
			for(j=0;j<6;j++){
				if(ar[i][j] && (row[i] == 3 && col[j] == 4) || (row[i] ==4 && col[j] == 3))
				{
					found =1;
					goto print;
				}
			}
		}
		print:
		if(found == 1) cout<<"correct\n";
		else cout<<"incorrect\n";
	}
	return 0;
}
